                <div class="desc">
                  <h3 class="name">Nell Shamrell</h3>
                  <small class="title">Senior Developer at PhishMe</small>
                  <div class="further"><a class="bio" href="#"><span class="icon icon-info"></span>Bio</a><a class="twitter" href="http://www.twitter.com/nellshamrell" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-twitter"></span>Twitter</a><a class="github" href="http://www.github.com/nellshamrell" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-github"></span>GitHub</a></div>
