                <p>During this talk we will walk through two very old Rails features—Active Record’s scopes and HTML sanitisation<span class="ellipsis">…</span><span class="sr-only">—and explain how they work under the hood. Also, It will be presented the current issues we’ve been facing and how they can be improved.</span></p>
